MELBA COCHRAN DICK, formerly MELBA COCHRAN, and MRS. CHESTER C. DOBBS, formerly CLARA COCHRAN, v. EVA L. GRANT. 23 So. (2nd) 495

June Term, 1945

October 5, 1945 Division B Fogle & Kirtley, for appellants. Frank E. Bryant, for appellee. *443PER CURIAM:

The decree appealed from is affirmed. E. B. Elliott Co., et al., v. Elliott, 137 Fla. 456, 188 So. 89.

It is so ordered.

CHAPMAN, C. J., BROWN, THOMAS and SEBRING, JJ., concur.
